x86/paravirt: Move the Xen-only pv_mmu_ops under the PARAVIRT_XXL umbrella

Most of the paravirt ops defined in pv_mmu_ops are for Xen PV guests
only. Define them only if CONFIG_PARAVIRT_XXL is set.

